	measure '# Cases (Monthly)' = ```
			
			SWITCH( [@ Data Source Label],
			    "health.gov.au",
			        CALCULATE( 
			            ADHAC[# Value ADHAC], 
			            ADHAC[Category] = "Cases" ,
			            ADHAC[Metric] = "Monthly Cases" 
			        ),
			    "NNDSS",
			        IF ( MAX( 'Dates'[Date] ) = MAX ( Dates[End of Month] ) ||
			                YEAR ( MAX( 'Dates'[Date] ) ) < CALCULATE( YEAR ( MAX( 'Dates'[Date] ) ), ALL ( 'Dates') ) ,
			            [# New Cases (NNDSS)],
			            [# New Cases (NNDSS)] / DAY( MAX ( 'Dates'[Date] ) ) * DAY ( MAX ( Dates[End of Month] ) )
			        )
			)
			```
		formatString: #,0
		lineageTag: 88fbc953-060f-4ab4-8d87-771fdd745273

		annotation PBI_FormatHint = {"isDecimal":true}

